divs: Sighting DetailsWas driving west on US 50 near Cisco, Utah about 02:05am when an amber disc rotating conter clockwise came up from behind a hill and was probably 200 feet in the air. The car shut off and lost all power and came to a stop in the midlle of the 2 lane road. LAst Iheard from am radio was the time - 2:08 am KSL am Salt Lake City Utah. The next I knew was leaning out the window watching something moving across the sky to the soutwest. The car tried to start and died as clutch was engaged. The radio was playing a song and then the DJ sad it was 2:44am Got car started and drove on.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Cisco
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Amber disc over hill lost time.
